window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Curators—Joe Ramsey, Grim, Lilli Spicer, Durango, and Lucius—have set up a headquarters in Richmond, London.</b></p> <p>Joe's new life becomes complicated when he learns that there's another grimoire out there, one that the Iron Order will do anything to obtain. Even leveling London.</p> <p>But Joe likes London.</p> <p>With his special ability to absorb magic and redirect it as he wills, he might just save it.</p>"; 
